{"tid":1871592,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有個識咗10年嘅朋友向我乞口罩，俾我屌到跪喺度喊","createTime":"2020-02-09T14:11:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T09:33:55.000Z","uid":150100,"like":255,"dislike":372,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"b9542852024e52fc973c4701f95946cdbacd926d","tid":1871592,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T14:11:24.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n今日約咗個兄弟出街食飯，個兄弟我中一frd到依家，識咗成10年<br />\n咁食食下飯佢就嚟料<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢：話說你搶唔搶到口罩？<br />\n我：搶到啲咁啦，本身有幾盒，網上訂嚟咗10盒，加埋出去排嗰啲都有十幾盒到<br />\n佢：咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可唔可以俾少少我<br />\n我：你冇咩？<br />\n佢：係，得返幾個咋，仲要返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我：哦，係咩？<br />\n佢：堅㗎，幫下手啦<br />\n我：俾咗你我仲點屌閪呀？宜家市價1Q20個，處女double，好貴㗎。我得嗰十幾盒，已經嫌少<br />\n佢：整少少嚟啦，頂多我俾錢你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我：你自己唔去搵？<br />\n<br />\n講到依刻佢已經開始眼濕濕<br />\n<br />\n佢：我已經試過網上訂，但係俾人cut單，hktvmall又幾秒冇曬，出街排通宵又得嗰幾個，返幾日工都用曬&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n去到依刻我實在忍唔住，一嘢喝鳩佢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你同我跪喺度！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢一嘢嚇到跪咗喺度，仲開始成個女人咁喊<br />\n<br />\n我：屌你老母臭閪，網上訂嘢都唔識，你弱智㗎？hktvmall幾秒就冇？咁你唔㩒快啲？屌你老母你小兒麻痺㗎？返工就用曬咁咪咪撚帶囉，你啲廢柴中肺炎死都抵啦。難得約出嚟食飯你問我攞口罩？你當我開善堂呀？係呀，我有口罩，但係就唔俾你，吹咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔駛返工唔駛出街，就日日坐喺屋企數口罩，你咬我食呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌到依度佢開喊到收唔到聲，仲開始窒息<br />\n<br />\n咁我見一場朋友，就廢事再屌落去<br />\n於是我放低兩個口罩，同佢講當我施捨佢，依餐就你嘅就走咗去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：樓主屌得好，依啲損友唔屌唔得<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我冇口罩，我係低能仔"},{"pid":"6660a2862c23aa2a550db1a6ba5fab762441f12b","tid":1871592,"uid":82829,"like":172,"dislike":6,"score":166,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T14:12:31.000Z","msg":"樓主低能仔🥱"},{"pid":"c157d44b31a68b6ae5d792bdad087fd63e9dfe02","tid":1871592,"uid":62469,"like":18,"dislike":4,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T14:14:09.000Z","msg":"個個好似你咁撚醒咩"},{"pid":"8bb83191113858e2d17f27e23fe7a58408695f01","tid":1871592,"uid":150100,"like":6,"dislike":12,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"c157d44b31a68b6ae5d792bdad087fd63e9dfe02","tid":1871592,"uid":62469,"like":18,"dislike":4,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T14:14:09.000Z","msg":"個個好似你咁撚醒咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T14:14:56.000Z","msg":"口罩都搶唔到醒極有限啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68956c3f3d989de4a8b4a8cb0c1fbe29359d7dc6","tid":1871592,"uid":150100,"like":3,"dislike":20,"score":-17,"quote":{"pid":"6660a2862c23aa2a550db1a6ba5fab762441f12b","tid":1871592,"uid":82829,"like":172,"dislike":6,"score":166,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T14:12:31.000Z","msg":"樓主低能仔🥱"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T14:15:23.000Z","msg":"我有13盒口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"989c312c77e11e283a1b1b35d8b3468d2102b56d","tid":1871592,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T14:16:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2bf0780ab966b5fc7428dfd2203fcd163eda9bd0","tid":1871592,"uid":4186,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"68956c3f3d989de4a8b4a8cb0c1fbe29359d7dc6","tid":1871592,"uid":150100,"like":3,"dislike":20,"score":-17,"quote":{"pid":"6660a2862c23aa2a550db1a6ba5fab762441f12b","tid":1871592,"uid":82829,"like":172,"dislike":6,"score":166,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T14:12:31.000Z","msg":"樓主低能仔🥱"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T14:15:23.000Z","msg":"我有13盒口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime